SAR

View CPU Statistics
sar -u 1 10

I/O Stats
sar -b 1 10

Disk Device Status
sar -d 1 5

Context switches:
sar -w 1 5


DSTAT

dstat --net --disk  --sys --load --proc --top-io-adv --top-cpu-adv
dstat -tldnpms 10

FATRACE report system wide file access events

# fatrace -f W
# fatrace -t -s 60 -o ~/fatrace.log
